creator: Robin Powered, Inc
descriptionHtml:
With Robin’s Android app, you can find spaces in your office fast to get your best work done.

This is a companion app to Robin, and your company must have an account set up.

As you walk into your office, book a desk to work from for the day right off an interactive map within the Robin app.

Get a glance at your daily schedule, with more detailed info on what conference rooms your meetings are taking place in.

Find an available meeting room on the fly without having to open your laptop, and review a room’s photo and amenities so you know exactly what to expect in the space.

A better workplace experience.
descriptionShort: Robin helps people do their best work.

Check the in-app changelog to see the latest changes.

- We've added a Help section within the settings menu to support any questions you have
- Changes made on Robin's web dashboard will now show up much faster in this app

title: Robin - Mobile App

creator: Robin Powered, Inc
descriptionHtml:
With Robin’s mobile app, you can find spaces and desks in your office fast to get your best work done.

As you walk into your office, book a desk to work from for the day right off an interactive map within the Robin app. Get a glance at your daily schedule, with more detailed info on what conference rooms your meetings are taking place in. Find an available meeting room on the fly without having to open your laptop, and review a room’s photo and amenities so you know exactly what to expect in the space.

Note: This is a companion app to Robin, and your company must have an account set up.
descriptionShort: This app is for people using Robin's meeting room and desk booking software.
